result.name: Tazmania Ballroom

reviews.text: Nice atmosphere and good service.
Always better if you know someone on the inside otherwise entry is not easy on busy nights if you’re brown skinned and don’t have female company

Most of the crowd here are regular patrons, being very loud and obnoxious, acting like they own the place.
Not a place to pick-up a date too - Was approached by a very flirty PH girl, who soon revealed that she was an escort looking for customers.
There are far better clubs nearby.
High-class lounge with pool tables and modern cocktails. Good crowd, not very loud, good vibes.  They deliver a standard experience to satisfy a diverse crowd.

Super cool night club for the swish set... pool tables, recessed booths and sparklers on bottles of you feel like spending extra cash, open air balcony in case you need your nicotine fix.
